ForecastNextMonth = Pronóstico (Next Mes)
SMAFormulaTitle = Media móvil simple
SMAFormulaDesc = SMA = Sum of last %s meses demand / %s. Equal weight to all periods.
WMAFormulaTitle = Media móvil ponderada
WMAFormulaDesc = WMA = Sum(qty x weight) / Sum(weights). Recent meses weighted more heavily (e.g. 3-month: weights 3,2,1).
SeasonalFormulaTitle = Índice estacional
SeasonalFormulaDesc = Índice estacional = Mes Average / Overall Mesly Average. Index > 1 means above-average demand for that month.
MAPEFormulaDesc = MAPE = error porcentual absoluto medio = (1/n) x Suma(|real - pronóstico| / real) x 100. Más bajo es mejor.
Month = Mes
Index = Índice
NoForecastData = Insufficient historical data for forecasting. Need at least %s meses of order/invoice history.

